1. **`extensions/pulseboard/package.json`** and **`extensions/pulseboard/openclaw.plugin.json`** -- Create first. These are leaf files with no code dependencies.

2. **`extensions/pulseboard/src/types.ts`** -- Create next. Defines the interfaces and account resolution functions used by `channel.ts`.

